e-8.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p><p><img src=\"attachment:20201219_173036george-turmanidze-img-20200427-063133-132.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h3><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/A9XbWe\">ArtStation - Bathroom Design, Ana Obradovic</a> </h3><section><p></p><p><img src=\"attachment:20201219_173459ana-obradovic-kupatilo-final2.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h3><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/n3y4o\">ArtStation - Mind Labyrinth VR Dreams - Scene 1, Andrea Marinelli</a> </h3><section><p></p><p><img src=\"attachment:20201219_173713andrea-marinelli-liv1-best.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p><p><img src=\"attachment:20201219_173725andrea-marinelli-liv1-best2.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h3><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/ybRDwO\">ArtStation - Assassin&apos;s Creed Odyssey : Fields of Elysium - Demeter&apos;s Dream, Vincent Gros</a> </h3><section><p></p><p><img src=\"attachment:20201219_182522vincent-gros-demetersdream005.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p><p><img src=\"attachment:20201219_182537vincent-gros-demetersdream007.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h2>Tue Feb 16 00:22:31 PST 2021</h2><section><p></p></section><h3><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/rRYwmE\">ArtStation - Winter Forest Lightning/Design Tests, Andrea Marinelli</a> </h3><section><p><img src=\"attachment:20210216_002250screenshot.png\">\n</p></section><h2>Feb 二月</h2><h3>家，环境，避世，清净，光亮</h3><section><p>其实从这些图中，能给我感觉到作家想要表达的那种感觉。画面里给我感受那种日光照射下，\n它过去时间的一个表达，和展现。青苔，松柏，\n</p><ul><li><p>Wed Feb 12 15:55:47 PST 2020\n</p></li></ul><p>其实我最开始我是<a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/XBwdvw\">ArtStation - CGPB培训班作品展示/ CGPB Mentorship Students\nShowcase, Donglu Yu</a> 的链接里看到的作品很喜欢就保存了下来\n</p></section><h4><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/fy-yako\">ArtStation - Feiyang Wang</a> </h4><section><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/KaDVeB\">ArtStation - Cats refuge, Feiyang Wang</a>\n</p><ul><li><p><img src=\"attachment:20200926_170934feiyang-wang-cats-shelter.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p></li></ul></li></ul></section><h4><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/49Q01\">ArtStation - Living Space, Mike Paolilli</a> </h4><section><p><img src=\"attachment:20200926_171057mike-paolilli-int-living-space-final.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h4><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/6gVzO\">ArtStation - Uncharted The Lost Legacy : Intro to Western Ghats , Rogelio Olguin</a> </h4><section><p><img src=\"attachment:20200926_171435rogelio-olguin-int-h-15.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h1>Cyberpunk</h1><h2><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/KqZ1y\">ArtStation - Cyberpunk Busy Street , Donglu Yu</a> </h2><section><p><img src=\"attachment:20200926_173359donglu-yu-cyberpunk-demo-lowres.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h2>❤ Love  <a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/Xag90\">ArtStation - Barcelona Smoke &amp; Neons: Sant Pau i La Sagrada Familia, Guillem H. Pongiluppi</a> </h2><section><p><img src=\"attachment:20200926_173420guillem-h-pongiluppi-guillemhp-barcelona-future-3.jpg.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h2><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/Z5gJ5N\">ArtStation - Cyberpunk Alley Environment, James Atkinson</a>    </h2><h1>City</h1><h2><a href=\"https://the-binary-tomorrow.tumblr.com/post/173454677836/theartofmany-artist-%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87%E6%96%AD%E4%BA%86-a-title-hi-chengdu\">theartofmany: Artist: 手指断了 a Title: Hi ChengDu ... - Our Sci-Fi Future</a> </h2><section><p><img src=\"attachment:tumblr_p7ikadfPzT1uzeyaxo3_1280.jpg\">\n</p></section><h2><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/EaaRn\">ArtStation - Half-Life - (February work), Wadim Kashin</a> </h2><section><p><img src=\"attachment:wadim-kashin-halflife1_2019-07-27_08-18-11.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h1>Science Fiction</h1><h2><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/artwork/NKYRD\">ArtStation - xcom , Eddie Del Rio</a> </h2><section><p><img src=\"attachment:eddie-del-rio-622709-10152191443342178-2030898129-o_2019-07-27_04-21-22.jpeg\">\n</p></section><h1>Environments</h1><h2><a href=\"https://www.artstation.com/